{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/film-slender-man-siap-menculik-para-penonton-di-tahun-ini/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Film Slender Man Siap Menculik Para Penonton Di Tahun Ini!","content":"<p>Karakter <em>horror video game</em> yang satu ini sangatlah populer. Awal kemunculannya bermula pada tahun 2009 di forum <em>something Awful</em>, dari seorang pengguna bernama Victor Surge. Sosok <em>Slender Man</em> digambarkan tinggi kurus dengan wajah kosong, mempunyai tentakel, dan mengenakan baju hitam berdasi merah.</p>\n<p>Karakter ini semakin dikenal lewat <em>storyline</em> yang beredar luas di internet. Diceritakan bahwa <em>Slender Man</em> sangat suka menculik atau melukai orang, terutama anak-anak. Lewat ke populeran itulah akhirnya <em>Slender Man</em> dibuat <em>video game</em>-nya pada bulan Agustus 2012 dengan judul <em>“Slender: The Eight Pages”.</em> <em>Game</em> ini pun mendapatkan sambutan yang bagus dengan jumlah <em>download </em>mencapai lebih dari 2 juta <em>download</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_38597\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-38597\" data-attachment-id=\"38597\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-slender-man-siap-menculik-para-penonton-di-tahun-ini/attachment/1-267/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-13.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: www.sonypictures.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: www.sonypictures.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-13.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-13.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-38597\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/1-13.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: www.sonypictures.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-38597\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: www.sonypictures.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Tahun 2018 memang menjadi tahun yang padat dengan film-film bagus, demikian juga untuk film-film ber-<em>genre</em> horor. <em>Slender Man</em> dipastikan tampil dalam film yang akan dirilis pada 18 Mei nanti. Baru-baru ini pihak <em>Sony Pictures Entertainment</em> selaku distributor, meng-<em>upload</em> <em>trailer</em> <em>Slender Man</em> lewat akun <em>Sony Pictures Entertainment</em>  di Youtube yang membuat banyak orang ketakutan.</p>\n<p>Berikut <em>trailer-</em>nya<em>:</em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ySy8mcceTno\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></em></p>\n<p><em>Slender Man</em> akan disutradarai langsung oleh Sylvain White. Sutradara asal Paris, Perancis ini, banyak dikenal orang lewat beberapa serial TV seperti “<em>Major Crimes</em>”, “<em>Sleepy Hollow</em>”, dan yang paling terbaru “<em>The Americans</em>”. Sedangkan untuk skenario akan ditulis oleh David Birke (penulis skenario film “<em>Elle</em>” dan “<em>13 Sins</em>”) dan sang kreator dari karakter <em>Slender Man</em> itu sendiri; Victor Surge.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_38594\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-38594\" data-attachment-id=\"38594\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-slender-man-siap-menculik-para-penonton-di-tahun-ini/attachment/2-208/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-13.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: www.sonypictures.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: www.sonypictures.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-13.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-13.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-38594\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/2-13.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: www.sonypictures.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-38594\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: www.sonypictures.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Melihat dari daftar <em>cast</em> yang akan bermain dalam film ini, nuansa horor <em>Slender Man</em> pasti akan tampil maksimal. Sebab para aktor dan artis yang terlibat hampir semuanya juga pernah terlibat dalam film-film horor ternama. Seperti Joey King yang pernah bermain dalam film “<em>The Conjuring</em>” sebagai Chrstine; Annalise Basso yang pernah menjadi karakter Lina Zander dalam film “<em>Ouija: Origin of Evil</em>”; serta Javier Botet, dalam film “<em>It</em>” sebagai Hobo.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_38591\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-38591\" data-attachment-id=\"38591\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-slender-man-siap-menculik-para-penonton-di-tahun-ini/attachment/3-232/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-13.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: www.sonypictures.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: www.sonypictures.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-13.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-13.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-38591\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/3-13.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: www.sonypictures.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-38591\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: www.sonypictures.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Premis <em>Slender Man</em> masih menggunakan cerita populernya tentang hilangnya anak-anak serta remaja secara misterius yang tidak lain diculik oleh sang <em>Slender Man</em>. Namun masih menjadi misteri besar mengapa <em>Slender Man</em> menculik anak-anak, kemungkinan hal ini akan terjelaskan nantinya dalam film ini.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_38588\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-38588\" data-attachment-id=\"38588\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-slender-man-siap-menculik-para-penonton-di-tahun-ini/attachment/4-223/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-13.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: www.sonypictures.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: www.sonypictures.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-13.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-13.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-38588\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/4-13.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: www.sonypictures.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-38588\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: www.sonypictures.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Suasana mencekam, adegan-adegan menegangkan, serta beberapa <em>jumpscare</em> yang diperlihatkan lewat <em>trailer-</em>nya, menunjukkan bahwa <em>Slander Man</em> akan menjadi film berkualitas yang wajib ditunggu para penikmat film horor.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_38585\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-38585\" data-attachment-id=\"38585\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/film-slender-man-siap-menculik-para-penonton-di-tahun-ini/attachment/5-226/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/5-12.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: www.sonypictures.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: www.sonypictures.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/5-12.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/5-12.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-38585\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/5-12.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: www.sonypictures.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-38585\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: www.sonypictures.com</p></div></p>\n<p>Penasaran dengan film ini? Kayak bro sis harus bersabar sambil berharap hasilnya nanti benar-benar maksimal dan gak mengecewakan, soalnya mayoritas <em>video game</em> yang diadaptasi menjadi film layar lebar akan berakhir buruk. Ah, semoga saja hal ini gak terjadi ya, pada <em>Slender Man</em>.</p>\n<p>Sudah siapkah kalian semua diculik oleh <em>Slender Man</em> bulan Mei nanti?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"4c7d193a-a9ec-5445-894e-805985438453"}}}